					    <meta itemprop=3D"position" content=3D"1">
					  </li></ol><h1 class=3D"entry-title" itemprop=3D"name headline">How t=
o Make a Yeast Starter</h1>

	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class=3D"entry-content" itemprop=3D"articleBody">

							<div class=3D"sr-only">Link to article</div>

		<figure class=3D"featured-image post-thumbnail ">


					=09
		=09
					<img alt=3D"yeast-starter-featured" src=3D"https://homebrewersassociat=
ion.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/yeast-starter-featured.jpg" itemprop=3D"=
image primaryImageOfPage" width=3D"600" height=3D"497" class=3D"img-fluid">
			=09
